Achievements.Name: Someone Get That Kid The Puck!
Achievements.Description: Play and score your 1st NHL goal in a regular season game in Be a Pro.

Achievements.Name: Elite
Achievements.Description: Grow your Be A Pro Character to 90+ Overall in Be a Pro.

Achievements.Name: That's Number 50!
Achievements.Description: Play and score your 50th NHL goal in a single season as a rookie in Be a Pro.

Achievements.Name: Lifting the cup
Achievements.Description: Win the Stanley Cup in Be A Pro mode.

Achievements.Name: Goose Egg
Achievements.Description: Play an entire game and have your 1st shutout in a NHL regular season game in Be a Pro.

Achievements.Name: Straight A's
Achievements.Description: Get straight As for coaching feedback in a game in Be a Pro.

Achievements.Name: Promoted
Achievements.Description: Get your Be A Pro Player promoted to the 1st line in the NHL in Be a Pro.

Achievements.Name: Drafted
Achievements.Description: Have your Be a Pro player drafted in Be a Pro mode while playing an entire season in the CHL.

Achievements.Name: Champions of the World
Achievements.Description: Play in and win the World Cup of Hockey.

Achievements.Name: Master Negotiator
Achievements.Description: Sign a 1st line Forward, a Top 2 Defenseman or an Elite Goalie during Free Agency in Franchise Mode.

Achievements.Name: Superstar
Achievements.Description: Make a trade to acquire a player with full Trade Value in Franchise Mode.

Achievements.Name: Hello Mr. President
Achievements.Description: Win the Presidents trophy in Franchise Mode.

Achievements.Name: Bring Home the Cup
Achievements.Description: Win the Stanley Cup in your first year after relocation in Franchise Mode.

Achievements.Name: Skipping Town as Champions
Achievements.Description: Win the Stanley Cup in the season prior to relocation in Franchise Mode.

Achievements.Name: Bobble Head Star
Achievements.Description: Score the hat trick goal with a player on their Bobble Head night in Franchise Mode.

Achievements.Name: Developer
Achievements.Description: Have a player that you drafted grow to 90+ overall in Franchise Mode.

Achievements.Name: Maximum Promos!
Achievements.Description: Have max in all stadium upgrades and promo nights in a single season in Franchise Mode.

Achievements.Name: League Champions
Achievements.Description: Be a member of an EASHL club that has recently won the League Title and return to the Seasons HUB

Achievements.Name: Conference Champions
Achievements.Description: Be a member of an EASHL club that has recently won a Division Title and return to the Seasons HUB.

Achievements.Name: On A Roll
Achievements.Description: Be a member of an EASHL club that had a perfect record last season and return to the Seasons HUB.

Achievements.Name: Victorious
Achievements.Description: Be a member of an EASHL club that has recently won a playoff cup and return to the Seasons HUB.

Achievements.Name: Promotions For All
Achievements.Description: Be a member of an EASHL club that has recently been promoted and return to the Seasons HUB.

Achievements.Name: Overtime Heroics
Achievements.Description: In an EASHL club game, score the game-winning overtime goal.

Achievements.Name: You'll Always Remember Your First
Achievements.Description: In an EASHL game, score your first goal as a skater or complete and win your first game as a goalie.

Achievements.Name: Veteran Club Members
Achievements.Description: Be a member of an EASHL club that has reached Level 25.

Achievements.Name: How Prestigious
Achievements.Description: Level up your EASHL pro past Player Level 50.

Achievements.Name: Suit up
Achievements.Description: Win a game as a user-controlled goalie in any mode.

Achievements.Name: Hat trick hero
Achievements.Description: Score 3 goals with one player while player or position locked.

Achievements.Name: Dish Master
Achievements.Description: Record 4 assists with one player while player or position locked.

Achievements.Name: Not My Bottle!
Achievements.Description: Knock off the opposing goalie's bottle from the net by scoring a goal.

Achievements.Name: Manual Sauce
Achievements.Description: Get an assist from a manual saucer pass in any mode.

Achievements.Name: Tee it up
Achievements.Description: Score a goal with a manual one timer in any mode.

Achievements.Name: Own the crease
Achievements.Description: Have a shutout and win a game as a user-controlled goalie in any mode.

Achievements.Name: This is my house
Achievements.Description: Manually execute a big shove in a net battle on a player when locked as a defender.

Achievements.Name: Great Escape
Achievements.Description: Successfully spin out of a net battle.

Achievements.Name: Just in Time!
Achievements.Description: Tie up a player with a net battle while a pass is already on its way to that player.

Achievements.Name: Complete Set
Achievements.Description: Complete a Hockey Ultimate Team Set for the first time.

Achievements.Name: Long Term Goals
Achievements.Description: Complete a Hockey Ultimate Team Master Set.

Achievements.Name: Season Veteran
Achievements.Description: Earn a promotion in a Hockey Ultimate Team Season.

Achievements.Name: Season Champion
Achievements.Description: Win the title in a Hockey Ultimate Team Season.

Achievements.Name: Undefeated
Achievements.Description: Win every game in a Hockey Ultimate Team Season.

Achievements.Name: Getting Crafty
Achievements.Description: Complete 50 Hockey Ultimate Team Sets.

Achievements.Name: Good Timing
Achievements.Description: Complete a limited time Hockey Ultimate Team Set.

Achievements.Name: Wheelin' And Dealin'
Achievements.Description: Buy and/or sell 150 items in the Hockey Ultimate Team Auction House.

Achievements.Name: Upgrade
Achievements.Description: Activate a Synergy Style in Hockey Ultimate Team.

Achievements.Name: Fully Operational
Achievements.Description: Have every player on your active Hockey Ultimate Team Lineup have an active Synergy Style.

Achievements.Name: With the First Overall Selection
Achievements.Description: Complete a Draft Champions Draft.

Achievements.Name: Draft Superstar
Achievements.Description: Win every game in a Draft Champions Draft.

Achievements.Name: Solid Selection
Achievements.Description: Draft a special player item in a Draft Champions Draft.
